   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sc204a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name>Columbia</name>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <date>30th April 1844</date>
               <salute>
                  <name>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Colo</abbr>
                        <expan>Colonel</expan>
                     </choice> Robert Allen</name>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Dr</abbr>
                     <expan>Dear</expan>
                  </choice> Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>by the advice of <name>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Govr</abbr>
                     <expan>Governor</expan>
                  </choice>. J. K. Polk </name> I inclose one <choice>
                  <orig>promisary</orig>
                  <reg>promissory</reg>
               </choice> note of <name>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Doct</abbr>
                     <expan>Doctor</expan>
                  </choice>. S.B. Pillow</name> for $20._ Due 4th <choice>
                  <abbr>Feby</abbr>
                  <expan>February</expan>
               </choice> 1839 which you will oblige me by collecting &amp; when collected pay yourself out of it and send me the balance by mail</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>Your compliance will oblige</salute>
               <salute>Yours Respectfully</salute>
               <signed>
                  <name>James Wilkins</name>
               </signed>
               <add>
                  <note>
                     <p>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>D</abbr>
                           <expan>Dear</expan>
                        </choice> Sir</p>
                     <p>
                        <choice>
                           <abbr>Capt</abbr>
                           <expan>Captain</expan>
                        </choice> James Wilkins is a neighboor of mine &amp; is a worthy man &amp; a good citizen. You will oblige me as well as him, by attending to the above request.</p>
                  </note>
               </add>
               <salute>Your friend</salute>
               <signed>
                  <name>James K. Polk</name>
               </signed>
               <add>
                  <name>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Col</abbr>
                        <expan>Colonel</expan>
                     </choice>. R. Allen </name>
                  <address>
                     <addrLine>
                        <name>Carthage <choice>
                              <abbr>Tn</abbr>
                              <expan>Tennessee</expan>
                           </choice>
                        </name>
                     </addrLine>
                  </address>
               </add>
               <pb n="2" facs="sc204b.small.jpg"/>
               <add>
                  <name>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Colo</abbr>
                        <expan>Colonel</expan>
                     </choice>. Robert Allen</name>
                  <address>
                     <addrLine>Carthage Tennessee</addrLine>
                  </address> mail</add>
            </closer>
         </div>
